Uasin Gishu Governor Jackson Mandago’s wife Lucy Mandago and some of last year’s election losers are among big guns battling for the Senate’s SRC slot. Other influential political figures seeking to sit as members of the Salaries and Remuneration Commission include KICC chairman and former South Mugirango MP Omingo Magara and immediate former Uasin Gishu Senator Isaac Melly. Others in the list published by Senate clerk Jeremiah Nyegenye include former Kakamega woman representative Rachel Ameso and former nominated Senator Halima Abdille. The 80 people in the list are battling for only one slot available for the Senate to nominate one person to represent county governments at the SRC. Click here for the latest political news